dc_title_s: Neighborhood Boundaries City of Milwaukee, WI 2007
dc_description_s: This data represents neighborhood boundaries for the City of Milwaukee, Wisconsin in 2007. [These files contain neighborhood boundaries, as defined by the Milwaukee Neighborhood Identification Project. The goal of the Neighborhood Identification Project is to define neighborhoods encompassing all of the residential areas in Milwaukee.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://data-mclio.hub.arcgis.com/
